{
  "stem": "9415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in-- was normal relationships.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not till the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, we heard about what's going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That the Jews were expelled from Germany, Polish Jews were expelled from Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we know that something was gonna happen at the end, but we wouldn't expect a war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the last year before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, as a matter of fact, a couple of friends of mine left for Israel at that time by illegal immigration.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But having a printing shop on my own at that time, and everything was going right, we didn't-- we didn't plan to leave Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the news from the press, what was going on, but we couldn't do much to do anything about.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course the Zionist organization say we should go, everybody, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as you know, the borders are-- were closed to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British didn't let in no Jews to Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to smuggle-- smuggled to come in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as long as you have a good house, a good business, it's not easy to leave everything and family to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, I was a member of the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE], the Bund, which says it really didn't.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, later I was working with [INAUDIBLE], the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they tried to send people to Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I didn't move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was still in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No pogroms.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe some places in the, let's say-- in some places maybe there were some actions against the Jews, single Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But was not pogroms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Jews wouldn't stand for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, we left Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard airplanes flying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just that time was the beginning of bombardment of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
